Class WadoRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pixelmed.web.WebRequest
      • com.pixelmed.web.WadoRequest

  • public class WadoRequest
extends WebRequest

    The WadoRequest class parses a DICOM PS 3.18 (ISO 17432), WADO URL into its constituent query parameters.
